data.description: Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home in the sought after neighborhood of Eagle Creek. This home features almost 2,000 sq. feet with a spacious open concept floor plan from living to kitchen and dining. With high ceilings and a split bedroom floor plan this home a must see and if you like to entertain this home is perfect! Private backyard with a gorgeous gunite swimming pool along with a large covered patio that makes it great for summertime fun!
